data.description: Fully updated Home! 3 bed 2 bath. Nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac. Enter into vaulted ceilings and an open kitchen and living area. Kitchen with brand new quartz counters and cabinets. Large bedrooms with updated baths and Vaulted ceilings.  Make this dreamy PNW home yours! Plenty of room to park your RV. Don't miss out on this move-in ready home. Community has an in ground pool and clubhouse and walking distance to River Park.
